data.description: Super cute cottage in the Garden District! This home is in great condition and has 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, slab foundation, fantastic front porch with swing, wood and ceramic flooring, tons of closet space, newer HVAC system ($16,000.00 value), roof is just 3 years old, attached rear garage, wrought iron fencing in the front yard, a fantastic rear courtyard with wood privacy fencing, Ring camera system, Nest thermostat, LED smart lighting, and radiant barrier insulation. Piano, washer, dryer, fridge, chest freezer, swing and patio furniture remain. All this and it's within walking distance of City Park and LSU lakes.* Interest Rate Buydown opportunity
